title: ASkyblock无法生成空岛世界
author: dadaee9
txt_content:
1.7.10 KC服 用的askyblock插件
输入/is
出现红字：
More set up is required before the plugin can start...
Edit config.yml. Then restart server.
Make sure you set island distance. If upgrading, set it to what it was before.


求大佬帮忙解决，谢谢

replies.author: Star小铭
replies.txt_content: 打开plugins里面的Askyblock中的config.yml文件，找到island distance的值，把他设为200

replies.author: dadaee9
replies.txt_content:
Star小铭 发表于 2019-6-9 19:38
打开plugins里面的Askyblock中的config.yml文件，找到island distance的值，把他设为200 ...
试过了，没用

换一个插件
或者找个空岛端把里面的插件挪出来
